title: Add the location 130,-140 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x5624c128b5e8f78bdfbd588f92d99138e8309feb (Esau)

## 🐲🐲 Next to Dragon City🐲🐲🐲

![🐲🐲 Next to Dragon City🐲🐲🐲](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/130/-140/map.png)

Should the scene located at 130,-140 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

The Venue is DCL's first authentic listening room. Users must hold MANA to enter, and only certain NFT's will allow users access to special events. This helps new users understand the true power of NFTs, and encourages them to hold MANA.

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=761c4630-3bfa-11ec-be0c-afec86cba5e5)**
author: 0x5E23D08324f017d5425e59A2782C9ae27aCE0958
